AlSharq App

- Pre Requirements
    -- install nodejs latest version
    -- run -> `npm install -g cordova`
    -- run -> `cordova --version` to make sure it's installed.
    -- run -> `npm install -g bower`
    -- make sure you have the right env for android

- Before Building
    -- cd into app folder then ...
    -- run -> `bower install`
    -- cd into www/js
    -- open App.js
    -- change the first line development -> production .. save and close

- Add Platforms
    -- cd into app folder then ...
    -- run -> `cordova platforms add android`
    -- run -> `cordova platforms add ios`

- Run on emulator
    -- run -> `cordova run android --target=targetName`
    -- run -> `cordova run ios --target=iPhone-5s`

- Run on Browsers
    -- run -> `cordova prepare`
    -- run -> `cordova serve`
    -- by defualt the app will be in localhost:8000

- Building
    -- run -> `cordova prepare`
    -- run -> `cordova build --debug android`
    -- run -> `cordova build --debug ios`

